item.dc:creator: @xxlegitxx xxlegitxx
item.description:
@xxlegitxx wrote:

dragonus18:

yes, there is a swastika, but its not JUST a nazi symbol, the swastika has been in use for over 3000 years, and is a symbol of power, do your research b4 you start hatin.

That is the Nazi symbol, just as Hitler described it in Mein Kampf. Red background, white disc, black swastika rotated 45 degrees. The rotated swastika in and of itself is heavily associated with Hitler and the Nazi party, but when you combine it with a red background and white circle, it is unmistakably Nazi. On another note, the swastika was mostly a sign of good luck and a symbol of the Hindu god, Brahma, usually not associated with power. I suggest you do your research before telling others to do likewise.
